what do you think i wrote these ages back and they're not my best murderer murderer walks on through the yard his face is cold and his eyes are hard and settles down beside a tree and frowns upon the dismal sea his hollow heart beats in its shell as he sits alone in a living hell and he thinks about her screams of fright she never even tried to fight he stood again and walked away as the rising sun announced the day and left behind beneath the ground the body which was never found murder blood drops on the brambles colouring the rose slippers on the flower bed someone has cold toes whispers in the corridor have you lost your voice red all down the river flows she left without a choice lie here i am in endless strife beneath the crimson skies which bleed into my heartless life and mingle with your lies the feild i'm in is green and lush like the envy in your soul and the poppies in their endless blush make you seem as black as coal please dont steal these ta x i was early when i wrote these and now am early but better than that at writing i should hope id be grateful for comments thanks for taking time to read these becky x by the way lol i go out all the time these are done in about minutes and publishing costs doesn't it s i dont know but thankyou for the comments you all rock wow powerfull emotional immerses the reader in deep thought great have a star u wrote this when you were wow great talent you should get published rav The Amber Spyglass Sin City Similarities between the Bible and the Qur'an Homunculi of Fullmetal Alchemist Kingdom Hearts The Shining (film) Social rule The Cure Blood Simple Shen Gong Wu Rei Ayanami Main characters of Fullmetal Alchemist Slayers Shaggy dog story Kingdom Hearts II Hellraiser The Catcher in the Rye Kill Bill Timeline of alternative rock Professional wrestling holds Doom enemies Kingdom Hearts: Chain of Memories The Star Wars Holiday Special Yoko Ono Leviathan Characters of The Sandman Kain (Legacy of Kain) Professional wrestling